      <div class="content-layer">
        <h2>READY FOR TAKEOFF?</h2>
        <p>Switch to the only GDS designed for the physics of modern travel.</p>
        <div class="input-group">
          <input type="email" placeholder="ENTER_EMAIL_COORDINATES" class="mono-input" />
